{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"minmax()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/minmax","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a>函数 <strong><code>minmax()</code></strong> 定义了一个长宽范围的闭区间，它与<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_Logical_Values_and_Writing_Modes\">CSS 网格布局</a>一起使用。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;inflexible-breadth&gt;, &lt;track-breadth&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>400px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>30%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> max-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>min-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 400px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>max-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>min-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;fixed-breadth&gt;, &lt;track-breadth&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>30%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>400px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> min-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> max-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;inflexible-breadth&gt;, &lt;fixed-breadth&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>400px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>30%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>min-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>max-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<p>此函数包含两个参数，<em>最小值</em> 和 <em>最大值</em>.</p>\n<p>每个参数分别是<code>&lt;length&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;percentage&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;flex&gt;</code>的一种，或者是<code>max-content</code>、<code>min-content</code>、或<code>auto</code>之一。</p>\n<p>如果 <em>最大值</em> &lt; <em>最小值</em>，则<em>最大值</em>被忽略并且<code>minmax(最小值,最大值)</code>被看成<em>最小值</em>。<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex_value\"><code>&lt;flex&gt;</code></a> 值作为最大值时设置网格轨道的弹性系数；作为最小值时无效。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"取值","title":"取值","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"length\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/length\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>非负长度。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"percentage\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\"><code>&lt;percentage&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>相对于列轨道中网格容器的内联大小的非负百分比，以及行轨道中网格容器的块长宽。如果网格容器的长宽取决于其轴的长宽，则<code>&lt;percentage&gt;</code> 必须取值为<code>auto</code>。<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/User_agent\">user agent</a> 可将轨道的内部长宽贡献调整为网格容器的长宽，并按将导致百分比达到的最小值来增加轨道的最终长宽。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"flex\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex_value\"><code>&lt;flex&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>单位为<code>fr</code>的非负维度，指定轨道弹性布局的系数值。每个<code>&lt;flex&gt;</code>长度的轨道都以其系数值比例均分剩余空间。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"max-content\"><code>max-content</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示网格的轨道长度自适应内容最大的那个单元格。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"min-content\"><code>min-content</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示网格的轨道长度自适应内容最小的那个单元格。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"auto\"><code>auto</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>作为最大值时，等价于 <code>max-content</code>。作为最小值时，它表示轨道中单元格最小长宽 (由<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/min-width\"><code>min-width</code></a>/<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/min-height\"><code>min-height</code></a>) 的最大值。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"正式语法","title":"正式语法","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">minmax( <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">[</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/length\" title=\"Possible values: a number followed by'em', 'ex', 'ch', 'rem', 'px', 'cm', 'mm', 'in', 'vh', 'vw', 'vmin', 'vmax', 'pt', 'pc' or 'px', like 3px, 1.5cm, -0.5em or 0\">&lt;length&gt;</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> min-content <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> max-content <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> auto <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">]</a> , <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">[</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/length\" title=\"Possible values: a number followed by'em', 'ex', 'ch', 'rem', 'px', 'cm', 'mm', 'in', 'vh', 'vw', 'vmin', 'vmax', 'pt', 'pc' or 'px', like 3px, 1.5cm, -0.5em or 0\">&lt;length&gt;</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex_value\" title=\"\">&lt;flex&gt;</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> min-content <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> max-content <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> auto <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Brackets: enclose several entities, combinators, and multipliers to transform them as a single component\">]</a> )</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">#container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>max-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> 150px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">box-sizing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> border-box<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #8cffa0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#container &gt; div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #8ca0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Item as wide as the content,<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n    but at most 300 pixels.\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Item with flexible width but a minimum of 200 pixels.\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Inflexible item of 150 pixels width.\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"result","title":"Result","isH3":true,"content":"<iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"示例\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"100%\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/minmax/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-grid/#valdef-grid-template-columns-minmax","title":"CSS Grid Layout Module Level 3"}],"query":"css.properties.grid-template-columns.minmax"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"css.properties.grid-template-columns.minmax","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/minmax/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参考","title":"参考","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>网格布局指南：<em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout#track_sizing_and_minmax()\">Basic concepts of grid layout - track sizing with minmax()</a></em></li>\n  <li>视频教程：<em><a href=\"https://gridbyexample.com/video/series-minmax/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Introducing minmax()</a></em></li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n  <li></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS\"><strong>CSS</strong></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Reference\"><strong>CSS 索引</strong></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout\">CSS 网格布局</a></li>\n  <li><strong>指南</strong>\n    <ol>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\">网格布局的基本概念</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Relationship_of_Grid_Layout\">与其他布局方法的关系</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Line-based_Placement_with_CSS_Grid\">基于线的定位</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas\">网格模板区域</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Layout_using_Named_Grid_Lines\">使用命名线布局</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Auto-placement_in_CSS_Grid_Layout\">网格布局中的自动定位</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Box_Alignment_in_CSS_Grid_Layout\">网格布局中的盒模型对齐</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_Logical_Values_and_Writing_Modes\">网格、逻辑值和书写模式</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_Layout_and_Accessibility\">CSS 网格布局和可及性</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_and_Progressive_Enhancement\">CSS 网格布局和渐进增强</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Realizing_common_layouts_using_CSS_Grid_Layout\">使用网格实现常见布局</a></li>\n    </ol>\n  </li>\n  <li><strong>属性</strong>\n    <ol>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid\">grid</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\">grid-area</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\">grid-auto-columns</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\">grid-auto-flow</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\">grid-auto-rows</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column\">grid-column</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-end\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-column-end (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-column-gap (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-start\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-column-start (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-gap (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row\">grid-row</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-end\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-row-end (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-row-gap (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-start\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-row-start (en-US)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\">grid-template</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\">grid-template-areas</a></li>\n      <li><a h